  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1069">
<l>iravuḷḷa vuḷḷa murukuṅ karavuḷḷa </l>
<l>vuḷḷatūu miṉṟik keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To think of (the evil of) begging is enough to melt one's heart; but to think of refusal is enough to break it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
